        <h1>Hello, my name <br>is Joel Goodman.</h1>
        <article>
            <p>I have been professionally designing and developing on the web since 2007, with a focus on higher
                education, food and beverage, creative professionals, and small businesses. I own <a
                    href="https://bravery.co/?utm_source=jgg">Bravery Media</a>, a digital strategy and
                design studio for higher education, and host the <a
                    href="https://thoughtfeederpod.com/?utm_source=jgg">Thought Feeder Podcast</a>.</p>
            <p>You can find me in Austin, TX.</p>
        </article>
